title: The Gary Coleman Show (Cartoon)
description: The Gary Coleman Show is an American animated television series, produced by Hanna-Barbera Productions that originally aired on NBC during the 1982-1983 season.[1] It featured the voices of Gary Coleman, Lauren Anders, Jennifer Darling, Julie McWhirter (who is credited as Julie McWhirter Dees), Geoffrey Gordon, LaShana Dendy, Jerry Houser, Calvin Mason, Sidney Miller, and Steve Schatzberg
